strings.Value: "You would like it in Absalom. It's a noisy city. Big."
"Heh, I wish I could trade my homeland for Absalom! And you'd probably be happy in my quiet village. But now â€“ oh well! Now we both have our home here, in the Stolen Lands!"
"I like visiting cities from time to time, but I'd rather sleep in a tent under the stars, than stare at stone walls."
"Oh yes, I'd like to go there! And maybe take the Test of the Starstone! Just imagine what a goddess I would make!"
